      h3(data-device-preview="../docs-demos/list-view-inset.html") Inset List Block
      p List blocks also could have inset (not fullwidth) styling. To make inset lost block just add "inset" class to "list-block":
      pre
        code
          | &lt;div class="list-block inset"&gt;
          |   &lt;ul&gt;
          |     ...
          |   &lt;/ul&gt;
          | &lt;/div&gt;          
      p It is also possible to make list inset only on iPad and keep it usual on iPhone. We need to use "tablet-inset" class for that:
      pre
        code
          | &lt;div class="list-block tablet-inset"&gt;
          |   &lt;ul&gt;
          |     ...
          |   &lt;/ul&gt;
          | &lt;/div&gt;          

